62611479.review:
Amazing game with artwork inspired by Ragnarok Online. This free Action RPG made with RPG Maker has a very good and touching story with easy to play mechanics. Even if you are not into Retro RPGs, you will enjoy the story and like the gameplay. The game is so good that it is quite a surprise that it is a free game, as there are many games on Steam that is not as good as this one and you have to pay to play them.

[u]Pros[/u]
+ Great story;
+ Easy controls and combat system;
+ Nice soundtrack;
+ Good artwork;
+ 3 different endings;
+ 6 hours of gameplay for free.

[u]Cons[/u]
- This game does not feature a "New Game +" system, so if you want play again and gather all the items, you will need to start at level 1;
- No Steam Cloud support.

