I don't think many people would agree with me on this, but this might just be my favourite story in a game ever. It's simple, yet so heartbreaking, and the endings and events are enough to make you cry. Easy gameplay even for people who usually don't play these types of games, relaxing to play with a great soundtrack in the background.

The game is short, but worth your time, and I definitely, absolutely recommend this game, you won't be dissapointed! 

Plus, it's free, so there's really nothing to lose here, just go and play it;

